===Tunisia===
{{Infobox
 |abovestyle = background:#cfc;
 |subheaderstyle = align-left
 |above        = {{Flagu|Tunisia}}
 |subheader    = Prostitution legal and regulated<br>Buying sex legal<br>Condoms mandatory<ref name="reveal" />
